NAME
    Perinci::CmdLine::Base::Patch::DumpAndExit - Patch
    Perinci::CmdLine::Base to dump object + exit on run()

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.01 of
    Perinci::CmdLine::Base::Patch::DumpAndExit (from Perl distribution
    Perinci-CmdLine-Base-Patch-DumpAndExit), released on 2014-12-14.

DESCRIPTION
    This patch can be used to extract Perinci::CmdLine object information
    from a script by running the script but exiting early after getting the
    object dump.

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Perinci-CmdLine-Base-Patch-DumpAndExit>.

SOURCE
    Source repository is at
    <https://github.com/perlancar/perl-Perinci-CmdLine-Base-Patch-DumpAndExi
    t>.

